Atlantic Express Corp.
is United States based company that offers full service logistics.

We operate on an international scale covering U.S., Canada, South and Central America, Eastern Europe, Far and Middle East, Africa. Company is licensed as Non-Vessel Operating Common Carrier (NVOCC) by the Federal Maritime Commission and approved by TSA to be Indirect Air Carrier.

OUR VALUES THAT GUIDE
OUR BUSINESS PROCESS

Customer Focus

With over 20 years in the business, we have won the trust of our customers by ensuring reliable, quality, and affordable freight forwarding services.

Efficiency

We made it our duty to bring the maximum benefit to our customers with the fastest delivery times and cost-effective solutions

Safety

We ensure the safety of the freight, entrusted to us, against all possible contingencies
